docs\reviews\session-recording\2026-04-27\1\raw\codex.stderr.log:4901:- **Session Recording** is a dedicated subsystem 
(`src/session-recorder.ts`, `src/session-replayer.ts`, `src/session-bundle.ts`, `src/session-sink.ts`, 
