`SessionReplayer.fromBundle/fromSource` receives a bundle with a `schemaVersion` it does not understand, OR a bundle 
with `engineVersion` whose `b`-component differs from the running engine (per A11.1 clause 9). Within-`b` mismatches 
warn but proceed. |
